		<lb n="4" break="no"/>vātu
	</p>

	<p>
		vāṇa-kō-<choice><orig>A</orig><reg>v-a</reg></choice>raicaru maru
		<lb n="5" break="no"/>-makkaḷ kan·ta-viṇṇa
		<lb n="6" break="no"/><unclear>ṉā</unclear>r kūṭal toṟu-k koṇṭa
