		<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṉ poṉ·ṉarampa<unclear>ṉā</unclear>r kol·laka-c
		<lb n="9" break="no"/>c<unclear>ē</unclear>vakaṉ<unclear>·</unclear> kākkaṇṭi Aṇṇāvaṉ kal
	</p>

	<p>
		<lb n="10"/>kūṭal Iḷa
		<lb n="11" break="no"/>-makkaḷ naṭuvi
		<lb n="12" break="no"/>tta kal
